:

1. *Million* ljudi na planeti je ugroženo siromaštvom. (A million people on the planet are threatened by poverty.)
2. Njegov ukupni prihod je bio više od *miliona* dolara. (His total income was more than a million dollars.)
3. On je odlučio da pokloni *milion* dolara nekoj humanitarnoj organizaciji. (He decided to donate a million dollars to some humanitarian organization.)
4. Država je izdvojila *milione* dolara za pomoć ugroženim stanovnicima. (The state allocated millions of dollars for help to the endangered inhabitants.)
5. Ova firma je zaradila *milion* dolara samo prošle godine. (This company earned a million dollars just last year.)